What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Although I believe everyone should take this course in order to understand the development of the next generation, I would recommend it to not only those who are interested in education, but also those who are interested in politics, policy, or government. Education is so crucial in our world and this class really brings the main issues to light! I love education and really dedicated myself to this class. Although I struggled at times, I have become a much stronger student because of this course.
